{"tid":1380771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實前線交戰緊嗰時，係咪應該搵人去參觀下政府建築物？","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:52:15.000Z","uid":270871,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"427717813ae921be92593b05d6c6ef8828a5a05d","tid":1380771,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"好似尋日咁<br />\n老實講多班人上前線都唔會由輸變贏<br />\n最多都只係退慢啲<br />\n當然前線愈多人，前線就安全<br />\n<br />\n不過尤其內街班和理非<br />\n如果可以去快閃參觀下政總狗竇<br />\n畫畫又好，起牆又好<br />\n班狗遲遲唔嚟嘅話甚至可以敲門拜訪下<br />\n係咪應該會好好多？<br />\n<br />\n就算唔講到圍魏救趙咁誇張<br />\n都可以等班官知道唔守就會俾人搞<br />\n於是班狗就以後都被迫分散部署<br />\n成日講be water但冇乜邊次真係實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043d8369b3f5a0b25c179ebcafa33fc6d7ea2e20","tid":1380771,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0743d5de35baed72e9d17546a19ed1b9ad364959","tid":1380771,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"c6d1dc0a368cb35e4c32eaa982650e616495e31d","tid":1380771,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"241bf4c2fcd8510bbb2448c7d0377dfeb856f644","tid":1380771,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ba7194d40e8ec1e38adc33bec99e84909262452e","tid":1380771,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"399b6f8c7e436dbc19ee99447e08546ffe49432f","tid":1380771,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid"